{"tid":2267442,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"幫口開解伊藤健太郎撞車事件，北野武惹網民反感被轟廢老","createTime":"2020-11-02T05:33:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-02T13:16:24.000Z","uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"17c592a38eea23ef0d775b9f0a7ce71b9af92401","tid":2267442,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T05:33:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zXEY7EU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzXEY7EU.png&h=eb2d30ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n23歲人氣男星伊藤健太郎，上星期在澀谷街頭與電單車發生碰撞不顧而去，令他惹上官非自毀前途。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CFJV9Tx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCFJV9Tx.png&h=86215bc1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n健太郎成為新聞人物，他獲釋後在傳媒面前鞠躬道歉，表示因自己引起的意外而影響到各位感到抱歉。對此，年屆72歲的名導北野武，前日在主持的電視節目上談論是次風波，可是北野武卻笑說：「都冇人感到受影響，呢邊不知幾開心，喺電視度睇得好過癮。」節目播出後，北野武的言論隨即引起網民反感，北野武更被批評是個「廢老」，還被勸早點退休。<br />\n<br />\n裡面更多內文<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201102/ONPIOZA4GRCPTDZ7ILMF6V55ZQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201102%2FONPIOZA4GRCPTDZ7ILMF6V55ZQ%2F&d=Vpe8FAkBT2vLq%2FWrgjLHxRZhTFX1FVJLw6RhI%2FCRHR8%3D&h=6e2909a5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201102%2FONPIOZA4GRCPTDZ7ILMF6V55ZQ%2F&h=761d5d30\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201102/ONPIOZA4GRCPTDZ7ILMF6V55ZQ/</a>"},{"pid":"fe48a978c2f580400207a6aa790b34433358341f","tid":2267442,"uid":38539,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T05:38:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/A7em5tw.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA7em5tw.gif&h=34614b6b&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\nmolamola<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b192345521d9de551cf4eebe28a1f0a3b7ec7395","tid":2267442,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike